  "texts": [
    "The theory on N D3-branes in the background of O3 + -plane has USp(2N) gauge group.",
    "Thus N = 4 SO(2N + 1) SYM theory is dual to N = 4 USp(2N) SYM theory.",
    "The O3 + -plane transforms under the T operation into O3 + -plane that carries 1/4 unit of D3-brane charge.",
    "While the theory on N D3-branes in the presence of O3 + still supports USp(2N) gauge group, it has a unit of theta-angle, which we call USp(2N) ′ theory.",
    "The O3 + -plane is invariant under the S transformation.."
